metadata.name: 1337 Ordinals Exchange Token #40
metadata.description:
1337 Ordinals is a collection of 69 original 1337 skulls made exclusively as Bitcoin Ordinals.

This token may be redeemed for the corresponding ordinal inscribed on Bitcoin.  Upon receipt of this token, 1337 skulls will transfer the corresponding ordinal to a designated bitcoin address.

View all of the 1337 Ordinals on the website: 
 https://1337skulls.xyz/ordinals

Follow 1337 skulls on Twitter:  https://twitter.com/1337skulls

More information can be found in the 1337 skulls discord: 
 https://discord.gg/1337skulls
